74
MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2006-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 31st January, 2006
11 Magha, 1927 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 31st January,
2006:-
i)
Dr. T. Subbarami Reddy relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of State Without Portfolio and assumed the charge of the
office of Minister of State in the Ministry of Mines.
Shri Jairam Ramesh relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of State Without Portfolio and assumed the charge of the
office of Minister of State in the Department of Commerce,
Ministry of Commerce & Industry; and +
ii)
iii)
Shri Dinsha J. Patil relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of State Without Portfolio and assumed the charge of the
office of Minister of State in the Ministry of Petroleum & Natural
Gas.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of the
Planning Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
